{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"main_10_level_main_10-07_end","storyGroup":"main_10","storySort":73,"storyDependence":"main_10_level_main_10-07_end","storyCanShow":0,"storyCode":"10-8","storyName":"无暇哀悼","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"号角再次痛失战友，决定救援被萨卡兹关押的其余士兵。而罗德岛与自救军也准备展开行动，救援落入萨卡兹之手的信使海蒂·汤姆森。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"obt/main/level_main_10-07_end","avgTag":"行动后","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"main_10-07","minState":"PASS","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":11,"next":13,"characters":["萨卡兹雇佣兵","赫德雷","？？？","蔓德拉","深池士兵","维多利亚士兵","号角","克洛维希娅","阿米娅","自救军战士","洛洛"]},"lines":[{"type":"HEADER","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"Dialog","id":1},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":2},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":3},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":4},{"type":"Character","id":5},{"type":"image","id":6},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":7},{"type":"Background","image":"27_g9_lightinduarea_street_d","screenadapt":"coverall","id":8},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$suspenseful_intro","key":"$suspenseful_loop","volume":"0.4","id":9,"musicid":0},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":10},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":11},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_053","id":12},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"萨卡兹雇佣兵","text":"头儿，你说得没错，我们跟丢了。","id":13,"figure":"avg_npc_053"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"萨卡兹雇佣兵","text":"那群反抗军......一个个的，比沙地兽还狡猾。就这一会工夫，他们就跟钻进沙堆里似的，完全没了影子。","id":14,"figure":"avg_npc_053"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_393_1#1$1","id":15},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"......的确。所以，不要浪费精力。","id":16,"figure":"avg_npc_393_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"在他们下一次冒头之前，守好你们的位置。","id":17,"figure":"avg_npc_393_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_053","id":18},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"萨卡兹雇佣兵","text":"好吧，头儿，你说了算。","id":19,"figure":"avg_npc_053"},{"type":"dialog","id":20},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_soldiersrun","volume":"1","id":21},{"type":"character","fadetime":"1","id":22},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":23},{"type":"Character","id":24},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"看来你找到了一批忠心耿耿的新属下，“头儿”。","id":25},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_393_1#1$1","id":26},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"他们相信这里会有好收成，这令他们满怀斗志。","id":27,"figure":"avg_npc_393_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","id":28},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"他们也很信任你。我看得很清楚，这份信任已经远超一名雇佣兵对另一名雇佣兵该有的程度。","id":29},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_393_1#1$1","id":30},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"这说明曼弗雷德的计划很奏效。","id":31,"figure":"avg_npc_393_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","id":32},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"你对他的评价很高。差点忘了，你们已经是推心置腹的好朋友了，对吧？他分给你的新居所，光是书房就比你之前住的院子还大。","id":33},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_393_1#7$1","id":34},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"......那间伯爵宅邸，它的主人正是死在我手上。","id":35,"figure":"avg_npc_393_1#7$1"},{"type":"Character","id":36},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"别告诉我你的良心在发烫。","id":37},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_393_1#2$1","id":38},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"当时他正在喝下午茶......他的妻子和三个孩子就坐在他面前。","id":39,"figure":"avg_npc_393_1#2$1"},{"type":"Character","id":40},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"......这的确不是我们过去接的那种活。但这是你自己选的，所以我们都没资格为我们死去已久的良心哀悼。","id":41},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_393_1#1$1","id":42},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"那就别问那样的问题。你想确认什么，直接看就好。你明明都知道。","id":43,"figure":"avg_npc_393_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","id":44},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"你压力很大，我难道就好过？","id":45},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"算了，不跟你说这些。眼下可不是向彼此寻求安慰的时候。我来找你，是想提醒你一句——多看看脚下。","id":46},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_393_1#1$1","id":47},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"你的意思是......","id":48,"figure":"avg_npc_393_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","id":49},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"雇佣兵总是没那么值得信任。","id":50},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"要是走路的时候不多注意一下影子动向的话，小心功亏一篑。","id":51},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_393_1#3$1","id":52},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"......你想告诉我的，就是这个？","id":53,"figure":"avg_npc_393_1#3$1"},{"type":"Character","id":54},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"不，不止。","id":55},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"我想说的是——兜兜转转这么久以后，她在路上了。","id":56},{"type":"dialog","id":57},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":58},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":59},{"type":"Character","id":60},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":61},{"type":"Background","image":"27_g9_lightinduarea_street_d","screenadapt":"coverall","id":62},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$nervous_intro","key":"$nervous_loop","volume":"0.4","id":63,"musicid":1},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":64},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_233_1#1","id":65},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蔓德拉","text":"我们的人都就位了吗？","id":66},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_406_1#1$1","id":67},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"深池士兵","text":"嗯，都按萨卡兹的意思，去那个地点......","id":68},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_233_1#2","name2":"avg_npc_406_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":69},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蔓德拉","text":"别犯傻了，我说的不是萨卡兹要我们做的事。","id":70},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_233_1#2","name2":"avg_npc_406_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":71},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"深池士兵","text":"长官，我们真的要在今晚行动吗？会不会......","id":72},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_233_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_406_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":73},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蔓德拉","text":"......你是想说，我们会不会中曼弗雷德的圈套？","id":74},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蔓德拉","text":"你以为我蠢到看不出他想做什么吗？","id":75},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_233_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_406_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":76},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"深池士兵","text":"没有，我不敢......","id":77},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_233_1#2","name2":"avg_npc_406_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":78},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蔓德拉","text":"他是想试探我，我也会让他试探。","id":79},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蔓德拉","text":"我们的人会任他调遣......但他不知道我们到底有几个人。","id":80},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_233_1#2","name2":"avg_npc_406_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":81},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"深池士兵","text":"所以，我们还是得好好帮萨卡兹守门？","id":82},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_233_1#7","name2":"avg_npc_406_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":83},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蔓德拉","text":"......住嘴。","id":84},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蔓德拉","text":"我非常讨厌这个说法，听起来就像我们是萨卡兹的......萨卡兹的......","id":85},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_233_1#8","name2":"avg_npc_406_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":86},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蔓德拉","text":"啧，算了。我们只需要忍这一天了。等办完这最后一件事，我们就离开伦蒂尼姆。","id":87},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_233_1#8","name2":"avg_npc_406_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":88},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"深池士兵","text":"真、真的吗？长官，那我们可太高兴了！","id":89},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"深池士兵","text":"我......我从小就很讨厌伦蒂尼姆，我的爸爸妈妈都是来了这里就没回去过......","id":90},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"深池士兵","text":"这个城市，它会吃人！","id":91},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_233_1#2","name2":"avg_npc_406_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":92},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蔓德拉","text":"......嗯。我也不喜欢这里。你见过哪一座城市像这样，有这么多地块，这么多高楼，这么多排水沟的吗？","id":93},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蔓德拉","text":"每次闻到那股......那股贵族餐桌上的油脂味，我都会犯恶心。","id":94},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蔓德拉","text":"好在，我们终于可以走了。","id":95},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蔓德拉","text":"传话下去，晚上都给我“好好表现”。绝对不能让曼弗雷德看出破绽。","id":96},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蔓德拉","text":"另外挑十个最能打的，跟着我行动。","id":97},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蔓德拉","text":"我让你跟着曼弗雷德......你看清楚他刚才去哪里了，没错吧？","id":98},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_233_1#2","name2":"avg_npc_406_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":99},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"深池士兵","text":"是的，长官。","id":100},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_233_1#1","id":101},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蔓德拉","text":"那就好。","id":102},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蔓德拉","text":"今天晚上......我一定要把我们的“间谍”救出来。","id":103},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蔓德拉","text":"我在伦蒂尼姆待了这么久，总要做成一件事，才好心安理得地回家吧？","id":104},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_233_1#5","id":105},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蔓德拉","text":"我......我才不会让领袖失望。","id":106},{"type":"dialog","id":107},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":108},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":109},{"type":"Character","id":110},{"type":"image","id":111},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":112},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_warehouse","screenadapt":"coverall","id":113},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$drift_intro","key":"$drift_loop","volume":"0.4","id":114,"musicid":2},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":115},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_422_1#1$1","id":116},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维多利亚士兵","text":"号角，你回来了！","id":117,"figure":"avg_npc_422_1#1$1"},{"type":"dialog","id":118},{"type":"character","id":119},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":120},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4039_horn_1#2$1","fadetime":"1","id":121},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":122},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"号角","text":"嗯。罗本他们呢？","id":123,"figure":"avg_4039_horn_1#2$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_422_1#1$1","id":124},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维多利亚士兵","text":"他们也早就回来了。","id":125,"figure":"avg_npc_422_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4039_horn_1#1$1","id":126},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"号角","text":"好。药找到了吗？我去看看萨利。","id":127,"figure":"avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_422_1#1$1","id":128},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维多利亚士兵","text":"你......你不用去了。","id":129,"figure":"avg_npc_422_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4039_horn_1#4$1","id":130},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"20","randomness":"70","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":131},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"号角","text":"怎么了？！你是说萨利他......","id":132,"figure":"avg_4039_horn_1#4$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4039_horn_1#2$1","id":133},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"号角","text":"......","id":134,"figure":"avg_4039_horn_1#2$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"号角","text":"我还是得去看看他。","id":135,"figure":"avg_4039_horn_1#2$1"},{"type":"dialog","id":136},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":137},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":138},{"type":"Character","id":139},{"type":"Text","text":"维多利亚又失去了一位好战士。","id":140},{"type":"Text","text":"一位可爱的姑娘也失去了一位好父亲。","id":141},{"type":"Text","text":"我们到底还要失去多少，才能看到这场悲剧的尾声？","id":142},{"type":"dialog","id":143},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":144},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4039_horn_1#5$1","id":145},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"号角","text":"......","id":146,"figure":"avg_4039_horn_1#5$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"号角","text":"萨利的女儿叫什么名字？艾琳，还是艾尔莎？我记得他们一家住在阿斯卡拉郡。","id":147,"figure":"avg_4039_horn_1#5$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"号角","text":"布莱克，麻烦你把萨利的遗物收起来，等战争结束，我们去一趟他家。","id":148,"figure":"avg_4039_horn_1#5$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4039_horn_1#5$1","name2":"avg_npc_422_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":149},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维多利亚士兵","text":"可是......他什么都没留下来。","id":150,"figure":"avg_npc_422_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4039_horn_1#5$1","name2":"avg_npc_422_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":151},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"号角","text":"......什么都没有留下来？","id":152,"figure":"avg_4039_horn_1#5$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"号角","text":"不，布莱克。他至少......留下了一段故事。我们还是得走一趟，他的女儿会想听一听......","id":153,"figure":"avg_4039_horn_1#5$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"号角","text":"我会告诉她，即使在最黑暗的时刻，她的父亲都从未向苦痛低头。","id":154,"figure":"avg_4039_horn_1#5$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4039_horn_1#5$1","name2":"avg_npc_422_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":155},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维多利亚士兵","text":"......好。我会陪你去，号角，我们等战争结束。","id":156,"figure":"avg_npc_422_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维多利亚士兵","text":"还有，萨利他给你留了一句话。","id":157,"figure":"avg_npc_422_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4039_horn_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_422_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":158},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"号角","text":"他......他说了什么？","id":159,"figure":"avg_4039_horn_1#4$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4039_horn_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_422_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":160},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维多利亚士兵","text":"他说——“中尉，对不起，但是请你活下去。”","id":161,"figure":"avg_npc_422_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4039_horn_1#5$1","name2":"avg_npc_422_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":162},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"号角","text":"......他向我道歉。","id":163,"figure":"avg_4039_horn_1#5$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4039_horn_1#5$1","name2":"avg_npc_422_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":164},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维多利亚士兵","text":"是的。而且，我理解他。我们都理解他。","id":165,"figure":"avg_npc_422_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维多利亚士兵","text":"作为一名士兵，我们都想过，有一天可能会在哪里战死。","id":166,"figure":"avg_npc_422_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维多利亚士兵","text":"可是经历了这么多以后，萨利他......不，我们都体会到了什么才更可怕。","id":167,"figure":"avg_npc_422_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维多利亚士兵","text":"看看如今的伦蒂尼姆，它明明是我们的家，却成了一座监狱。","id":168,"figure":"avg_npc_422_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维多利亚士兵","text":"对我们来说，光荣地战死，是不是已经成了一种奢望？","id":169,"figure":"avg_npc_422_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4039_horn_1#5$1","name2":"avg_npc_422_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":170},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"号角","text":"......本不该如此。","id":171,"figure":"avg_4039_horn_1#5$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4039_horn_1#5$1","name2":"avg_npc_422_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":172},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维多利亚士兵","text":"是啊，但事实就是如此。","id":173,"figure":"avg_npc_422_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维多利亚士兵","text":"我们明明都清楚这一点，却还是......还是想要你坚持下去，因为是你给了我们希望。","id":174,"figure":"avg_npc_422_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维多利亚士兵","text":"号角......你本来不用承担我们这么多人的希望。这太重了。","id":175,"figure":"avg_npc_422_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4039_horn_1#2$1","name2":"avg_npc_422_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":176},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"号角","text":"......","id":177,"figure":"avg_4039_horn_1#2$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"号角","text":"活下去......更难，是吗？","id":178,"figure":"avg_4039_horn_1#2$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"号角","text":"哈......看来我欠她一个道歉了。","id":179,"figure":"avg_4039_horn_1#2$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4039_horn_1#2$1","name2":"avg_npc_422_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":180},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维多利亚士兵","text":"她是谁？","id":181,"figure":"avg_npc_422_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4039_horn_1#2$1","name2":"avg_npc_422_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":182},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"号角","text":"她和你们一样，是最优秀的维多利亚士兵。","id":183,"figure":"avg_4039_horn_1#2$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"号角","text":"她......先不说这些。","id":184,"figure":"avg_4039_horn_1#2$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"号角","text":"告诉其他人，我们没时间哀悼了。","id":185,"figure":"avg_4039_horn_1#2$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4039_horn_1#2$1","name2":"avg_npc_422_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":186},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维多利亚士兵","text":"——！","id":187,"figure":"avg_npc_422_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维多利亚士兵","text":"号角，你找到被关押的其他士兵的下落了？","id":188,"figure":"avg_npc_422_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4039_horn_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_422_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":189},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"号角","text":"几率很大。","id":190,"figure":"avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"号角","text":"如果我问出来的消息属实，萨卡兹明天上午就会把人都转移走。","id":191,"figure":"avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"号角","text":"我本来......我打算问一下你们的意见。","id":192,"figure":"avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4039_horn_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_422_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":193},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"维多利亚士兵","text":"号角，你不需要问，请直接下令吧！","id":194,"figure":"avg_npc_422_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4039_horn_1#1$1","id":195},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"号角","text":"好。等到天黑，我们立刻行动。","id":196,"figure":"avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":197},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":198},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":199},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":200},{"type":"Character","id":201},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":202},{"type":"Background","image":"27_g6_hideout","screenadapt":"coverall","id":203},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":204},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":205},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$ponder_intro","key":"$ponder_loop","volume":"0.4","id":206,"musicid":3},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_401_1#6$1","id":207},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"克洛维希娅","text":"最有可能的关押位置我已在地图上标明了，诸位还有没有什么看法？","id":208,"figure":"avg_npc_401_1#6$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_394_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_401_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":209},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"还剩下......八个地点吗？","id":210,"figure":"avg_npc_394_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"就算加上我们的干员，想在两天之内排查完全部地点，也还是挺困难的。","id":211,"figure":"avg_npc_394_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_394_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_401_1#6$1","focus":"2","id":212},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"克洛维希娅","text":"很遗憾，这八个地点全都符合作为临时监狱的条件。","id":213,"figure":"avg_npc_401_1#6$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"克洛维希娅","text":"它们附近都没有居民聚集区，这意味着很难有消息传入传出。","id":214,"figure":"avg_npc_401_1#6$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"克洛维希娅","text":"它们同时也都位于通往中央区的干道附近，这方便萨卡兹士兵在内外城区之间往来。","id":215,"figure":"avg_npc_401_1#6$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"克洛维希娅","text":"以及......它们都并不与我们所在的地块连通。","id":216,"figure":"avg_npc_401_1#6$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_394_1#5$1","name2":"avg_npc_401_1#6$1","focus":"1","id":217},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"萨卡兹的指挥官猜到了你们会在地下活动？","id":218,"figure":"avg_npc_394_1#5$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_394_1#5$1","name2":"avg_npc_401_1#8$1","focus":"2","id":219},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"克洛维希娅","text":"他很聪明，我们绝不能小瞧他。","id":220,"figure":"avg_npc_401_1#8$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_394_1#3$1","name2":"avg_npc_401_1#8$1","focus":"1","id":221},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"那......既然是用来关押俘虏的地方，是不是理应有重兵把守？","id":222,"figure":"avg_npc_394_1#3$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_394_1#3$1","name2":"avg_npc_401_1#6$1","focus":"2","id":223},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"克洛维希娅","text":"我们也考虑过。","id":224,"figure":"avg_npc_401_1#6$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"克洛维希娅","text":"很遗憾，我们的侦察人员追踪了萨卡兹士兵在各个区块的行动路线，但都没有发现破绽。","id":225,"figure":"avg_npc_401_1#6$1"},{"type":"dialog","id":226},{"type":"character","id":227},{"type":"Decision","options":[{"id":"229","text":"这个位置是什么地方？"}],"values":[],"id":228},{"type":"Predicate","references":["1"],"id":229,"end":234},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_401_1#6$1","id":230},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"克洛维希娅","text":"一家废弃工厂。以前据说是炼糖用的......对了，请不要误会，这只是流传在民用工业地带的一种俗称。","id":231,"figure":"avg_npc_401_1#6$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"克洛维希娅","text":"他们炼制的是一种名为扭转醇的有机化合物，只是因为包装与深受孩子们喜爱的糖果近似，大家才戏称他们在“炼糖”。","id":232,"figure":"avg_npc_401_1#6$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_394_1#5$1","id":233},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"炼糖厂？听起来好耳熟......","id":234,"figure":"avg_npc_394_1#5$1","end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":235},{"type":"character","id":236},{"type":"Decision","options":[{"id":"238","text":"请把这里列为首要排查的目标。"},{"id":"238","text":"我们或许接近答案了。"}],"values":[],"id":237},{"type":"Predicate","references":["1","2"],"id":238,"end":240},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_401_1#5$1","id":239},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"克洛维希娅","text":"{@nickname}博士，能让我知道为什么吗？","id":240,"figure":"avg_npc_401_1#5$1","end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":241},{"type":"character","id":242},{"type":"Decision","options":[{"id":"244","text":"我们可能认识这家炼糖厂的主人。"}],"values":[],"id":243},{"type":"Predicate","references":["1"],"id":244,"end":248},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_394_1#5$1","id":245},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"啊......我想起来了。您是说......托马斯先生？","id":246,"figure":"avg_npc_394_1#5$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"托马斯先生一直在为萨卡兹干活，对不对？他说他看见萨卡兹在利用他的炼糖厂做一些事，而且他还因此差点被萨卡兹灭口。","id":247,"figure":"avg_npc_394_1#5$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"再加上深池......深池也想要托马斯先生身上的情报。","id":248,"figure":"avg_npc_394_1#5$1","end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":249},{"type":"character","id":250},{"type":"Decision","options":[{"id":"252","text":"所有站在萨卡兹对立面的势力都想要......"},{"id":"252","text":"......萨卡兹不希望别人得到的情报。"}],"values":[],"id":251},{"type":"Predicate","references":["1","2"],"id":252,"end":258},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_401_1#6$1","id":253},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"克洛维希娅","text":"我明白了。","id":254,"figure":"avg_npc_401_1#6$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_401_1#6$1","id":255},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"克洛维希娅","text":"通知费斯特，我们的第一目标是制醇厂。","id":256,"figure":"avg_npc_401_1#6$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_401_1#6$1","id":257},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"克洛维希娅","text":"哈默，你们的转移工作继续，我们依然随时做好两手准备......","id":258,"figure":"avg_npc_401_1#6$1","end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":259},{"type":"character","id":260},{"type":"delay","time":"0.51","id":261},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$rungeneral","volume":"0.9","id":262},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_398_1#1$1","fadetime":"1","id":263},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":264},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"自救军战士","text":"指挥官！","id":265,"figure":"avg_npc_398_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_401_1#4$1","id":266},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"克洛维希娅","text":"怎么了，劳伦斯？","id":267,"figure":"avg_npc_401_1#4$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_398_1#1$1","id":268},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"自救军战士","text":"侦察小队回来了，他们在地面上遇到了萨卡兹雇佣兵——","id":269,"figure":"avg_npc_398_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_401_1#4$1","id":270},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"克洛维希娅","text":"......伤亡如何？","id":271,"figure":"avg_npc_401_1#4$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_398_1#1$1","id":272},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"自救军战士","text":"四人负伤，一人......被俘。","id":273,"figure":"avg_npc_398_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_401_1#6$1","id":274},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"克洛维希娅","text":"抱歉了各位，会议中止，我得去看看......","id":275,"figure":"avg_npc_401_1#6$1"},{"type":"dialog","id":276},{"type":"character","id":277},{"type":"delay","time":"0.51","id":278},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":279},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4040_rockr_1#10$1","fadetime":"1","id":280},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":281},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛洛","text":"......指挥官。","id":282,"figure":"avg_4040_rockr_1#10$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_398_1#1$1","id":283},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"20","randomness":"70","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":284},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"自救军战士","text":"洛洛，你怎么来了？你的伤口才刚包扎好！","id":285,"figure":"avg_npc_398_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4040_rockr_1#1$1","id":286},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛洛","text":"不......我有消息要亲口告诉指挥官。","id":287,"figure":"avg_4040_rockr_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_401_1#3$1","name2":"avg_4040_rockr_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":288},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"克洛维希娅","text":"你们难道找到了......","id":289,"figure":"avg_npc_401_1#3$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_401_1#3$1","name2":"avg_4040_rockr_1#10$1","focus":"2","id":290},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛洛","text":"是的，我们得到了戈尔丁女士的消息。她还在北部居民区的学校里，她很安全......","id":291,"figure":"avg_4040_rockr_1#10$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛洛","text":"但他们在两天前的一场聚会中，遭到了萨卡兹的突袭。","id":292,"figure":"avg_4040_rockr_1#10$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛洛","text":"信使女士她......被捕了。","id":293,"figure":"avg_4040_rockr_1#10$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_401_1#6$1","name2":"avg_4040_rockr_1#10$1","focus":"1","id":294},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"克洛维希娅","text":"......","id":295,"figure":"avg_npc_401_1#6$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_394_1#5$1","id":296},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"请等一下——","id":297,"figure":"avg_npc_394_1#5$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name"